lead_paragraph: Daniel Sturridge sent Liverpool into the League Cup quarter-finals and gave his manager a reminder of his talents with two clinical goals in a 2-1 win over Tottenham Hotspur on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Sturridge Brace Helps Liverpool Down Spurs, Arsenal Through
